      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's easy to say \"start anew\" but i don't see how. i've burned every bridge and spent every cent. the shame is just... it's heavy. it feels like a physical weight. everyone thinks i'm this big innovator and now i'm just a fraud who ruined everything. there is no \"rebuilding\" from this much damage. it feels like the only way to actually stop feeling this pathetic is to just not exist anymore.",
