      "content": "it's not about small steps. it's about the fact that the damage is permanent. the debt, the reputation, the way my family looks at me... it's all broken. a \"quiet step\" doesn't fix the fact that i've failed everyone. everything just feels so terminal. like there's no version of the future where this doesn't follow me everywhere. it would just be so much more peaceful if the story ended here instead of dragging this out for years of misery.",
